  "description": "A nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with vibrant fireworks. The scene features a long bridge stretching across dark water, leading towards a densely packed cityscape. The skyline is dominated by numerous buildings, some appearing as illuminated towers. Above the city, colorful fireworks explode in various shades of red, white, and blue, creating a dazzling display against the dark sky. The water below reflects some of the city lights and the fireworks, creating a shimmering effect. The overall composition emphasizes the scale and beauty of the urban landscape combined with the celebratory atmosphere of the fireworks.",
